    "substantially longer text.",
    "We measure the average number of tokens 9 in generations from our fine-tuned models (Suri-I-ORPO and Suri-SFT) and compare them to baseline models, including Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.2, Llama-3-8B-Instruct (AI@Meta, 2024), and Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1 (Jiang et al., 2024).",
    "For faster inference, we use vLLM (Kwon et al., 2023) to generate outputs from the backtranslated instruction x w.",
